snippet.title: Crescent Loom Trailer #1
snippet.description:
KICKSTARTER DATE ANNOUNCED: January 31 2017!
Crescent Loom is Kerbal Space Program crossed with the cell stage of Spore. Wire up neurons into circuits to control little wriggling beasties and explore an alien world.

To get updates:
http://facebook.com/wickglyph
http://twitter.com/wickglyph
http://tinyletter.com/wick

Music:
"Improbable" -- Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
